**Evaluate an Organizations Data Security Posture**


About this learning activity:

In this capstone project, you will evaluate the data security posture for Cedarville Family Health, a Rhode Island healthcare provider. The aim is
to identify and address potential issues in data and information security and compliance with Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act
(HIPAA) regulations. 


Learning objectives

After completing this capstone project, you should be able to: 

Evaluate data security and privacy
Assess risk
Develop a plan for backup
Apply file and drive encryption 
